      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the M96/03 3.6L flat-six, utilizing VarioCam Plus for an optimized power band and linear throttle response. The G96 6-speed manual transaxle remains precise, paired with a dual-row ceramic IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced Rear Main Seal (RMS). The chassis is well-sorted with Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, maintaining factory-spec kinematics. While the exterior shows minor road patina, the vehicle excels mechanically with a leak-free crankcase and consistent compression across all cylinders. It represents a mechanically robust, driver-focused example of the analog 911 experience.",
